===Noun===
'''pirate''' (plural: [[pirates]])

# one who [[rob]]s ships while at sea; a [[nautical]] [[bandit]]
# (''internet'') one who reproduces [[copyright]]ed works without [[permission]] for the purpose of [[distributing]] them to others for free

===Verb===

# (''internet'') to obtain, usually by downloading from a [[file sharing]] [[network]], an [[unauthorized copy]] of [[software]] or other works
#:''Not willing to spend full price for the game, Heidi instead pirated a copy''

